STATE of North Carolina
v.
Edwin Christopher LAWING No. 217P18-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2019 Nicholaos Vlahos, Assistant Attorney General, For State of North Carolina. Edwin Christopher Lawing, For Lawing, Edwin Christopher. N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 5th of July 2019 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Wake County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
